{"tid":852184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（精忠報國）新華社：香港未來十年基建總投資將超萬億港元","createTime":"2018-10-07T16:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T02:56:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"683e1ac131b4e6be30b900f23c2b02c5b0d7b650","tid":852184,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:04:19.000Z","msg":"據新華社報導，香港特區政府政務司司長張建宗7日表示，特區政府未來十年在基礎設施建設上總投資將超過一萬億港元；張建宗預計，未來五年，香港每年的整體建造工程量會維持在2500億港元至3000億港元的高水平，包括機場三跑道系統建設工程、房屋發展、中九龍幹線及醫院發展計劃等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20181007/28400078.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20181007%2F28400078.html&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEyghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=84877e38\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20181007/28400078.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b4c7e11489212896e13fa731a24e5f91a520b14","tid":852184,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:05:12.000Z","msg":"未計人工島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b171a40b8e7fb60cf8ef504f8fa8ec9e9fc8a854","tid":852184,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔派錢俾香港人，但係派錢俾贏國"},{"pid":"cf411b0a930cfffb09eb30b53f6414c279445815","tid":852184,"uid":54733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"工程撚表示發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食政府條水都夠飽,唔怕貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0667f11c2fdcd8005f133a194c7cc68e1696e91d","tid":852184,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf411b0a930cfffb09eb30b53f6414c279445815","tid":852184,"uid":54733,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:26:29.000Z","msg"